Djibouti
- 2 cVDPV2 positive environmental samples were reported; 1 each in the provinces of Djibouti and Arta. There are 5 positive environmental samples reported in the country, linked to the virus circulating in Yemen.

Democratic Republic of the Congo (DR Congo)
- No case of circulating vaccine-derived poliovirus type 2 (cVDPV2) was reported this week. The total number of 2021 cases remains at 25.

